Package: BreastCancerModules
Title: Calculates Gene Expression-Based Modules Curated in the Perou Lab
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Matthew", "Sutcliffe", , "matthew_sutcliffe@med.unc.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This R package calculates gene expression module scores from gene expression data, particularly for breast cancer research. It includes a curated collection of approximately 1000 biologically-relevant modules compiled from the literature, which can be used in differential expression analysis and other genomic analyses instead of individual genes. The package supports median-based calculations, centroid-based correlations, and more complex models.
